Therefore, "Xã Yên Hóa" is now part of "Xã Minh Hóa, Tỉnh Quảng Trị." I then referenced the `New wards` list to confirm and obtain the corresponding ward code. I found "Xã Minh Hóa, Tỉnh Quảng Trị" with the code "18901."

Finally, I built the JSON output: the new ward is "Xã Minh Hóa," code is "18901," province is "Tỉnh Quảng Trị," with a "high" confidence level (due to the explicit nature of the resolution).
